  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_162",
    "english": "Showing promising skills in an evil demonic cult, one can join a higher rank. Proving their fanatical loyalty and faith toward the cult, they obtain power enough to go against the demons of the Demon Realm by reinforcing and transforming their bodies with spells. They personally carry out the will of the cult, and punish those non-believers and heretics if needed.",
